        <p>This is “The Administrator” its version also known as “Adminique Beta”. It is a very simple display of administrative features that are digitized. Features such as: </p>
        <h3>Asset Management</h3>
        <p>Sometimes you may need to have the information of the value of your assets available at hand. Use "The Administrator" to display a present-day oversight of your assets.</p>
        <h3>Budget Management</h3>
        <p>You might use or need a planned monthly budget. For a quick oversight of or a unique perspective on your monthly budget, you use "The Administrator".</p>
        <h3>Financial Planning for Payments</h3>
        <p>If you would like a quick oversight of bills to pay and/or expected payments, this feature of "The Administrator" might be just what you need.</p>
        <h3>Administration of Hours</h3>
        <p>Are you busy with your administration of hours? Or would you simply like to reflect on the way your time is divided? "The Administrator" has got you covered.</p>
        <h3>Notabilities</h3>
        <p>There could be dozens of incoming and outgoing expenses in your account(s) every month. Sometimes, for administrative purposes or purposes of general reflection, you may want to view some expenses that are of special value. To view this is a feature of "The Administrator".</p>
